<Project Sdk="Microsoft.NET.Sdk">

  <PropertyGroup>
    <TargetFramework>netstandard2.0</TargetFramework>
    <Version>2.16.0-alpha</Version>
    <Description>Wrapper for getopenwater.com REST APIs. Full featured read/write API for the most popular application and review platform.</Description>
    <GeneratePackageOnBuild>true</GeneratePackageOnBuild>
    <PackageLicenseExpression>MIT</PackageLicenseExpression>
    <PackageId>OpenWater</PackageId>
    <Authors>OpenWater</Authors>
    <Company>OpenWater</Company>
    <Product>OpenWater</Product>
    <PackageIconUrl></PackageIconUrl>
    <PackageReleaseNotes>PLEASE READ CAREFULLY BEFORE UPDATING PACKAGE. THIS VERSION CONTAINS BREAKING CHANGES.

Changelog:
 + Renamed `SchedulerTargetType` enum to `SchedulerEventTargetType`

* Breaking changes (order of arguments has changed):
  - [Fields]:
    + ApplicationNameFieldModel: `firstTitle`, `secondTitle` arguments become optional
    + FileUploadFieldModel: `allowedFileExtensions`, `captionLabel` arguments become optional
    + LetterOfRecommendationFieldModel: `confirmationPageHtml` argument becomes optional
    + MultilineTextFieldModel: `allowedHtmlTags` argument becomes optional
    + NumberFieldModel: `format` argument becomes optional
    + TableFieldModel: `rowName`, `rowNamePlural` and `rowTemplate` arguments become optional.
 
  - [Request models]:
    + ChangeFinalizedRoundSubmissionStatusRequest: `status` argument becomes required.

  - [Field values]:
    + LetterOfRecommendationFieldValueModel: `email`, `fullName` arguments become optional.

* Not breaking changes:
 - [Field values]:
    + AddressFieldValueModel: `city`, `countryCode`, `line2`, `line3`, `state`, `street` and `zip` arguments become optional
    + ApplicationNameFieldValueModel: `firstValue`, `secondValue` arguments become optional
    + DigitalSignatureFieldValueModel: `value` argmuent becomes optional
    + FileUploadFieldValueModel: `caption` argument becomes optional
    + ImisNumberFieldValueModel: `result`, `value` arguments become optional
    + SessionNameFieldValueModel: `value` argument becomes optional
    + TextFieldValueModel: `value` argument becomes optional
    + WysiwygFieldValueModel: `value` argument becomes optional.

 - [Misc]
    + Fixed DateTimeOffset handling on HTTP GET requests, when DateTime formatted in UTC instead of local without timezone.</PackageReleaseNotes>
    <PackageIcon>icon.png</PackageIcon>
  </PropertyGroup>

  <ItemGroup>
    <Compile Update="OpenWaterApiClient.Generated.cs">
      <DependentUpon>OpenWaterApiClient.cs</DependentUpon>
    </Compile>
  </ItemGroup>

  <ItemGroup>
    <PackageReference Include="Newtonsoft.Json" Version="9.0.1" />
  </ItemGroup>

  <ItemGroup>
    <Folder Include="Models\Generated\" />
  </ItemGroup>

  <ItemGroup>
    <None Include="icon.png">
      <Pack>True</Pack>
      <PackagePath></PackagePath>
    </None>
  </ItemGroup>
</Project>
